  "body": "**Problem:**\r\nI finished to sync my eth fullnode and run it since a month now. As you can see in the following pictures, my main problem now is that the CPU usage is permanently between 100-300%, even though i have 24-core and 200GB of RAM! I just tried to restart the import with \"systemctl start geth\" but it immediately goes back to 100-300% CPU usage.\r\n\r\n\r\n**System:**\r\nGeth version:  1.9.17-stable\r\nOS & Version: Ubuntu 18.04.4 LTS\r\nServer hardware: 24-core - 200GB RAM\r\n\r\n\r\n**After full sync:** \r\n![1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222921-9a48a480-082b-11eb-86b1-99bbc659cc5b.JPG)\r\n![2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222928-9caafe80-082b-11eb-9b7d-86dc6949af20.JPG)\r\n![3](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222940-9e74c200-082b-11eb-8da2-102d1f092880.JPG) \r\n \r\n\r\n**Stop after full sync:**\r\n![1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95223014-b0eefb80-082b-11eb-84f1-d41ec95cf46b.JPG)\r\n![2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95223018-b2202880-082b-11eb-89cf-921f59316ef9.JPG) \r\n\r\n\r\n**Restart after stop from full sync:**\r\n![1](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222963-a3397600-082b-11eb-8aea-7d16b68378e3.JPG)\r\n![2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222989-aa608400-082b-11eb-8add-09c5dde8fb0b.JPG)\r\n![3](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42303143/95222998-ac2a4780-082b-11eb-966a-6f92927dca48.JPG)\r\n",
